{"tid":1195263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由頭到尾，香港人都無俾大台騎劫","createTime":"2019-06-09T14:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T16:08:14.000Z","uid":101154,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a77c10f6dcb17b50d6df2abe52e3c09e46c0c1","tid":1195263,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwhm1eG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqwhm1eG.png&h=9f47b3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2:30由維園出發，暫時一個政黨都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBEgP8G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBEgP8G.png&h=736d8ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一過sogo,成班大台吸血鬼已經出黎大叫林鄭林鄭，市民和應完之後就立即顯露原形，要人捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問條路係咪泛民/民主黨/社民連交路費俾我地遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反我認為民陣先有需要我地捐款<br />\n大台係前面灣仔至老銅賺一筆之後，你金鐘有無見到任何一個大台帶領市民同警察對峙？<br />\nSorry, 係無。我由九點至十點係夏慤道等等等<br />\n等來既係一批批警察<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8yNcrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8yNcrL.png&h=72e4bbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCugQds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCugQds.png&h=472d1f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由邊個帶領市民叫開路？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27j1gTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27j1gTR.png&h=38963cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只不過係我地一班小市民自發<br />\n由頭到尾，行前面只有中學生，大學生，比較年輕的一輩<br />\n上次叫佢地衝，今次唔通又叫佢地衝？<br />\n作為一個政黨，連小小力量都組織唔到，只係識發國難財<br />\n你話，養班廢物有乜撚野用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，香港人今次真係抵讚，一呼百應<br />\n垃圾雖然好多，但大路上無乜。只係垃圾桶旁邊亂哂<br />\n其他國家一定會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好灰心，有下一次都要再出去<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">改變始於人民</span></span><br />\n切記： <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚再捐錢俾大台</span></span>"},{"pid":"658af68e9d26cb1a3b22f02229f360633212f275","tid":1195263,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"[再唔衝就玩完] 海富多速龍 轉場去立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1195131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1195131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57493a376f636409b03c4af54a4c9bf7425054c3","tid":1195263,"uid":101154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"長毛： 我地開始架啦<br />\n反送中 ～ 反送中<br />\n林鄭林鄭林鄭~ <br />\n下面d靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 多謝大家支持"},{"pid":"5bdc21d65c3cb4b8b652a09ff715d7e0f15d989e","tid":1195263,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"push <br />\n要更加多人知道，大台都係賊"},{"pid":"626807be3ba4a52607653365a98870f5f47de0d4","tid":1195263,"uid":239104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"好嬲 cap水就過主啦 <br />\n除左叫人捐款就係成個機械咁: 林鄭！下台！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455c33b442b1de57c2bbd1023e0dd7e6ac57781a","tid":1195263,"uid":121866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"cap水都算 唔緊要呀 你情我願<br />\n大佬你唔好淨係識收錢先得架<br />\n你班政棍渣住支咪係用黎領導群眾 唔係用黎講多謝<br />\n開路都係靠自己開 班政棍仲係度叫林鄭林鄭林鄭"},{"pid":"9530506f82b8c5194cb2f19112dbb0571483a150","tid":1195263,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"屌那星真係on99<br />\n明明終點先最需要有人lead住<br />\n班撚樣就淨係識喺前半段cap水鳩叫 當正71咁"},{"pid":"5761cd65559b7b41ce3661f590f6207038420916","tid":1195263,"uid":